20treasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20UK%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20ruled%20that%20salvage%20company%20Argentum%20Exploration%20doesn't%20have%20a%20salvage%20fee%20claim%20for%20recovering%20%2443%20million%20of%20silver%20from%20the%20wreck%20of%20the%20SS%20Tilawa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArgentum%20Exploration%20is%20majority-owned%20by%20British%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20Paul%20Marshall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tilawa%20was%20sunk%20by%20a%20Japanese%20submarine%20under%20mysterious%20circumstances%20just%20off%20the%20Seychelles%20Islands%20in%201942%2C%20killing%20280%20people%20and%20sending%20its%20silver%20cargo%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ship%20had%20been%20transporting%20the%20silver%20from%20Bombay%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20where%20it%20was%20to%20be%20used%20to%20mint%20coins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fprogrammes%2Fw3ct4xg2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20dubbed%20the%20ship%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Indian%20Titanic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Argentum%20Exploration%20sent%20specialist%20salvage%20vessels%20a%20mile%20and%20a%20half%20down%20to%20the%20site%20to%20gather%20the%20silver.%20It%20was%20then%20brought%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20the%20legal%20battle%20over%20salvage%20fees%20unfolded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20silver%20belongs%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20Argentum%20Exploration%20said%20that%20it%20was%20entitled%20to%20a%20claim%20for%20salvage.%20In%20international%20maritime%20law%2C%20salvage%20companies%20can%20make%20such%20a%20claim%20even%20if%20they%20weren't%20commissioned%20by%20the%20legal%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20South%20Africa%20said%20it%20was%20immune%20from%20that%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20turned%20on%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20silver%20was%20in%20commercial%20use%20at%20the%20time%20it%20was%20lost%20%E2%80%94%20which%20would%20have%20removed%20the%20country's%20immunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20earlier%20rulings%20sided%20with%20Argentum%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20the%20UK's%20Supreme%20Court%20disagreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bcargo%20sitting%20in%20the%20hold%20of%20a%20ship%20is%20not%20being%20used%20for%20any%20purpose%2C%20commercial%20or%20otherwise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20illustrates%20the%20complex%20and%20often%20high-stakes%20international%20legal%20wranglings%20that%20surround%20shipwrecks%20and%20precious%20salvage%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftreasures-lost-at-sea-kept-by-finders-or-us-government-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20Business%20Insider's%20Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20ruling%2C%20the%20judges%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20two%20parties%20had%20arrived%20at%20a%20private%20settlement%20last%20month%2C%20without%20giving%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20parties%20have%20agreed%20that%20we%20should%20nevertheless%20hand%20down%20the%20judgment%20and%20we%20are%20satisfied%20that%20it%20is%20appropriate%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%20is%20subject%20to%20a%20non-disclosure%20agreement%2C%20Ross%20Hyett%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Argentum%20Exploration%2C%20told%20BI.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20ruling%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20important%20judgment%20clarifying%20the%20law%20on%20sovereign%20immunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarshall%2C%20Argentum's%20majority%20owner%2C%20also%20co-owns%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritain-anti-woke-gb-news-ceo-interview-angelos-frangopoulos-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGB%20News%2C%20a%20self-styled%20anti-%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20news%20outlet%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20UK%20in%20the%20mold%20of%20Fox%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyett%20told%20BI%20that%20Marshall%20had%20no%20input%20into%20the%20running%20of%20Argentum%2C%20or%20its%20dealings%20with%20the%20South%20African%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalvage-firm-loses-case-43m-in-shipwrecked-silver-indian-titanic-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715263366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663ca429b4abc992e8c73052%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalvage-firm-loses-case-43m-in-shipwrecked-silver-indian-titanic-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Argentum%20Exploration%20lost%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20South%20Africa%20over%20salvage%20fees%20for%20%2443%20million%20in%20silver%20bars%20it%20pulled%20from%20the%20wreck%20of%20the%20SS%20Tilawa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mia%20Jankowicz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalvage-firm-loses-case-43m-in-shipwrecked-silver-indian-titanic-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Janhvi%20wears%20dress%20with%20cricket%20balls%3A%20WATCH%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715263218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109985611%2Cimgsize-68836.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjanhvi-kapoors-dress-with-cricket-balls-steals-the-show-as-she-promotes-mr-and-mrs-mahi-with-rajkummar-rao-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F109985567.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109985567.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJanhvi%20Kapoor%20promotes%20her%20upcoming%20film%20'Mr%20and%20Mrs%20Mahi'%20with%20Rajkummar%20Rao.%20As%20the%20film%20largely%20is%20about%20cricket%2C%20the%20a