EIf%20you%20looked%20under%20the%20dinner%20table%20at%20my%20grandfather%2C%20you'd%20see%20him%20holding%20a%20bottle%20of%20vinegar%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20a%20piece%20of%20bread%20in%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20condiment%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediterranean-diet-what-everyone-should-make-shopping-list%5C%22%3EMediterranean-diet%20staple%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20easy%20swap%20for%20just%20about%20any%20sauce.%20You%20can%20switch%20out%20ranch%20dressing%20for%20some%20oil%20and%20vinegar%20on%20your%20salads%20or%20add%20the%20ingredient%20to%20your%20soups%20to%20give%20them%20a%20lighter%20and%20tangier%20flavor.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20versatility%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealth-benefits-apple-cider-vinegar-2018-1%5C%22%3Ebenefits%20of%20vinegar%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20made%20it%20a%20family%20staple%2C%20one%20that%20I%20hypothesize%20added%20years%20to%20my%20grandparent's%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20don't%20drink%20it%20or%20douse%20my%20soups%20with%20it%20as%20some%20family%20members%20do%2C%20I%20appreciate%20it%20as%20an%20easy%20swap%20for%20dressings%20and%20sauces%20that%20would%20otherwise%20weigh%20down%20a%20refreshing%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwap%20your%20sandwiches%20for%20soups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20whip%20up%20a%20monotonous%20ham-and-cheese%20sandwich%20during%20a%20lunch%20rut%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-the-trick-to-make-quick-healthy-soup-from-jessica-biel%5C%22%3Emaking%20soup%20the%20main%20star%20of%20a%20meal%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20pack%20your%20dish%20with%20protein%20and%20veggies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20would%20pass%20around%20popular%20Mediterranean%20options%20like%20lentil%2C%20bean%2C%20and%20Greek%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%2C%20which%20features%20lemon%20and%20egg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20meals%20are%20thrown%20together%20with%20the%20same%20base%2C%20which%20is%20made%20by%20saut%C3%A9ing%20chopped%20celery%2C%20onions%2C%20and%20carrots%20in%20some%20olive%20oil%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20sometimes%20pepper%20or%20parsley%20until%20soft.%20Plus%20keeping%20these%20ingredients%20on%20hand%20means%20you'll%20never%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20what%20to%20make%20for%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPair%20the%20finished%20meal%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20bread%20and%20a%20chunk%20of%20cheese%2C%20and%20you're%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrecut%20a%20variety%20of%20fruit%20for%20easy%20breakfasts%20and%20desserts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223033%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fruit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6058be37138e680019ad9309%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222275%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20enjoy%20a%20cup%20of%20fresh%20fruit%20as%20a%20breakfast%20side.%3Cp%3EHanasch%2FShuttershock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20you're%20following%20a%20Mediterranean%20diet%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20can't%20enjoy%20dessert.%20You%20can%20pair%20a%20scoop%20of%20ice%20cream%20with%20a%20ton%20of%20fruit%20and%20nuts%2C%20like%20a%20vanilla%20base%20with%20peaches%20and%20pecans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20way%20of%20eating%20includes%20a%20rich%20variety%20of%20fruits%2C%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20up%20your%20intake%20early%20in%20the%20day%20by%20having%20a%20precut%20cup%20as%20a%20breakfast%20side%20instead%20of%20just%20sprinkling%20a%20few%20blueberries%20on%20your%20cereal%20or%20oatmeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20cut%20out%20all%20alcohol%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20that%20a%20glass%20or%20two%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrinking-health-benefits-heart-nutrition-2019-10%5C%22%3Ered%20wine%20can%20actually%20be%20healthy%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20commonly%20held%20belief%20in%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20wine%2C%20we%20sometimes%20enjoy%20a%20shot%20or%20two%20of%20whiskey%20or%20ouzo%2C%20a%20strong-flavored%20and%20licorice-like%20alcohol%2C%20before%20dinner.%20You%20easily%20can%20swap%20your%20after-work%20beers%20for%20these%20alternatives%2C%20which%20typically%20are%20less%20calorically%20dense.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeppers%20are%20a%20versatile%20and%20delicious%20ingredient%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223548%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stuffed%20peppers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6058c01797a4660018280d0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222661%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeppers%20come%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20colors%20and%20flavors.%3Cp%3EKrzysztof%20Slusarczyk%2FShuttershock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather%20would%20often%20tell%20strangers%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20relatives%20alike%20that%20he%20credited%20his%20healthy%20gut%20to%20peppers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHungarian%20wax%20peppers%20are%20one%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediterranean-diet-what-everyone-should-make-shopping-list%5C%22%3Efamily's%20favorites%20for%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20you%20can%20easily%20stuff%20them%20with%20ground%20meat%20and%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20a%20go-to%20condiment%20of%20ours%20is%20basically%20a%20combination%20of%20tomato%20sauce%20and%20peppers%20that%20you%20can%20use%20to%20elevate%20meals%20that%20might%20otherwise%20not%20include%20vegetables%20%E2%80%94%20my%20family%20would%20even%20add%20it%20to%20fast-food%20cheeseburgers%20and%20pizza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20easily%20make%20your%20own%20roasted%20peppers%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20range%20from%20mil