nded%20up%20being%20one%20of%20my%20favorites%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20enjoy%20everything%20I%20tried%2C%20but%20the%20highs%20outshined%20the%20lows.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223249%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plater%20of%20short%20ribs%20on%20a%20wooden%20serving%20tray%20at%20fogo%20do%20chao%20steakhouse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6634f61dec0c69656900ba5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222437%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20beef%20ribs%20were%20amazing.%20%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20meat%20that%20came%20my%20way%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20misses%20of%20the%20entire%20meal.%20It%20was%20a%20hunk%20of%20chicken%20that%20I%20found%20dry%2C%20tough%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20overcooked.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20eased%20it%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20plate%20after%20one%20bite%20and%20had%20some%20more%20street%20corn%20and%20soup%20to%20cleanse%20my%20palate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFortunately%2C%20the%20next%20gaucho%20brought%20total%20redemption%20in%20the%20form%20of%20more%20chicken%20(this%20time%20wrapped%20in%20bacon)%20and%20small%2C%20tender%20cuts%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-ways-to-cook-different-steak-cuts-from-chef-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebacon-wrapped%20steak%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20is%20usually%20the%20case%20with%20bacon-wrapped%20foods%2C%20both%20the%20chicken%20and%20the%20beef%20were%20excellent%20%E2%80%94%20tender%20and%20flavorful%20with%20just%20enough%20fattiness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20the%20filet%20mignon%20was%20pleasant%20enough%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-popular-chef-best-ribs-recipe-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeef%20ribs%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20outstanding.%20I'd%20never%20eaten%20a%20bite%20of%20meat%20that%20was%20so%20crisp%20(almost%20crunchy)%20on%20the%20outside%20but%20melt-in-your-mouth%20tender%20on%20the%20inside.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20trend%20of%20hits%20and%20misses%20continued%20throughout%20the%20meal.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223357%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22skewer%20of%20meat%20on%20a%20table%20at%20fogo%20de%20chao%20steak%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6634f93fec0c69656900bfbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222518%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20meats%20that%20made%20the%20entire%20meal%20worth%20it%20on%20their%20own.%20%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20only%20had%20one%20bite%20of%20the%20lamb%20(I'm%20not%20the%20biggest%20fan)%2C%20but%20I%20kept%20reaching%20for%20the%20picanha.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-steaks-for-grilling%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprime%20cut%20of%20sirloin%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20tender%20inside%20with%20a%20charcoal-smoked%20crust%20that%20was%20salty%20and%20rich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20no%20surprise%20to%20me%20that%20one%20server%20identified%20this%20as%20the%20restaurant's%20most%20popular%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20at%20least%20three%20other%20types%20of%20meat%2C%20but%20none%20of%20them%20were%20that%20notable.%20Nearly%20at%20capacity%2C%20I%20closed%20out%20the%20meal%20with%20another%20serving%20of%20picanha%20and%20a%20polite%20but%20firm%20rejection%20of%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20my%20meal%2C%20I%20literally%20wasn't%20hungry%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plate%20of%20food%20from%20fogo%20de%20chao%20steak%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6634f6b810dfcda409666ffe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20h