20vehicles%20sold%20during%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coxautoinc.com%2Fnews%2Fcox-automotive-forecast-april-2024-u-s-auto-sales-forecast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECox%20Automotive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20Hyundai's%20offering%20in%20this%20crucial%20segment%20has%20been%20the%20Tucson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20the%20strikingly%20stylish%20Tucson%20has%20not%20only%20evolved%20into%20the%20brand's%20best-selling%20model%2C%20with%20nearly%20210%2C000%20units%20sold%20in%202023.%20It's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20models%20in%20the%20segment%2C%20in%20its%20fourth%20generation%20that%20launched%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20recently%20spent%20a%20week%20with%20a%202024%20Hyundai%20Tucson%20Hybrid%20Limited%20AWD%20around%20the%20roads%20of%20suburban%20Atlanta%20to%20see%20why%20it's%20so%20popular%20with%20buyers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20end%20of%20a%202024%20Hyundai%20Tucson%20Hybrid%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a5d67ec0c69656901df63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202024%20Hyundai%20Tucson%20Hybrid%20Limited%20has%20a%20quiet%20cabin.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20impressed.%20The%20Tucson%20Hybrid%20is%20a%20great%20little%20SUV%20with%20a%20quiet%20cabin%2C%20comfortable%20ride%2C%20loads%20of%20tech%2C%20peppy%20performance%2C%20and%20futuristic%20looks.%20But%20it%20isn't%20perfect%20%E2%80%94%20The%20unrefined%20engine%20and%20transmission%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20annoyance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SUV%20is%20available%20in%20traditional%20internal%20combustion%20(ICE)%20form%2C%20as%20a%20hybrid%20(HEV)%2C%20and%20as%20a%20plug-in%20hybrid%20(PHEV