s%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20remained%20tense%20since%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20claimed%20in%20the%20country's%20Parliament%20in%20September%20last%20year%20that%20his%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20allegations%26quot%3B%20linking%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20in%20June%202023%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20India%20had%20been%20given%20any%20evidence%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20reiterated%20the%20country's%20consistent%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMincing%20no%20words%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20first%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20no%20specific%20or%20relevant%20evidence%20or%20information%20has%20been%20shared%20by%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20in%20regard%20to%20this%20matter%20till%20date.%20You%20will%20therefore%20understand%20our%20view%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20being%20pre-judged.%20Obviously%2C%20there%20are%20political%20interests%20at%20work.%20We%20have%20long%20maintained%20that%20separatists%2C%20extremists%20and%20those%20advocating%20violence%20have%20been%20given%20political%20space%20in%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20diplomats%20have%20been%20threatened%20with%20impunity%20and%20obstructed%20in%20their%20performance%20of%20duties.%20We%20have%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20that%20figures%20associated%20with%20organised%20crime%20with%20links%20with%20India%20have%20been%20allowed%20entry%20and%20residency%20in%20Canada.%20Many%20of%20our%20extradition%20requests%20are%20pending.%20We%20are%20having%20discussions%20at%20the%20diplomatic%20level%20on%20all%20these%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Brar%2C%2022%2C%20Kamalpreet%20Singh%2C%2022%2C%20and%20Karanpreet%20Singh%2C%2028%2C%20residents%20of%20Edmonton%2C%20were%20arrested%20last%20week%20on%20suspicion%20of%20being%20part%20