ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-is-expensive-people-annoyed-eating-out-restaurant-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomers%20who%20say%20they're%20tired%20of%20rising%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-fast-food-is-so-much-more-expensive-value-affordable-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Es%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20diners%20say%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-california-expensive-diners-could-switch-to-chilis-applebees-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswitching%20to%20casual-dining%20chains%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20what%20they%20describe%20as%20a%20better%20sit-down%20experience%20with%20higher%20quality%20food%20for%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20just%20a%20few%20extra%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20if%20it%20is%20winning%20over%20some%20fast-food%20customers%2C%20Applebee's%20sales%20are%20still%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplebee's%20reported%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.dinebrands.com%2Fstatic-files%2F13b74c39-8df1-4361-b6f3-77f32a7afb4b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4.6%25%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20US%20same-restaurant%20sales%20for%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20which%20it%20attributed%20to%20a%20decrease%20in%20traffic.%20Its%20US%20restaurants%20brought%20in%20an%20average%20of%20%2454%2C700%20in%20sales%20each%20a%20week%2C%20down%20from%20%2456%2C800%20for%20the%20same%20quarter%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-prices-increases-consumers-weary-mcdonalds-wendys-starbucks-kfc-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFast%20food%20chains%20McDonald's%2C%20Wendy's%2C%20and%20Burger%20King%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20said%20that%20their%20comparable%20sales%20are%20growing%20at%20a%20much%20slower%20rate%20than%20this%20time%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ddf4f35-b7e8-48d7-a3e9-1320332b3ee3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiners%20are%20hungry%20for%20deals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDine%20Brands%20CEO%20Peyton%20told%20investors%20at%20the%20company's%20earnings%20call%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20about%2028%25%20of%20Applebee's%20orders%20in%20the%20quarter%20were%20tied%20to%20a%20limited-time%20offer%20or%20promotion%2C%20up%20from%20about%2019%25%20in%20the%20same%20period%20in%202023%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20consumer%20has%20become%20more%20price%20sensitive%2C%20as%20indicated%20by%20the%20response%20to%20our%20limited-time%20promotions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplebee's%20Whole%20Lotta%20Bacon%20Burger%20promotion%20was%20a%20time-limited%20deal%20that%20launched%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.dinebrands.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fapplebees-launches-new-whole-lotta-bacon-burger%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApril%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20provided%20diners%20with%20bacon-loaded%20cheeseburgers%20and%20a%20side%20%E2%80%94%20fries%20as%20the%20default%20%E2%80%94%20for%20%249.99%20for%20both%20dine-in%20and%20to-go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20the%20burger%20cost%20between%20%2413.99%20and%20%2419.99%20at%20the%20locations%20Business%20Insider%20looked%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20promotions%20Applebee's%20has%20launched%20so%20far%20this%20year%20include%20its%20All%20You%20Can%20Eat%20promotion%20in%20January%2C%20which%20Peyton%20said%20%26quot%3Bexceeded%20our%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapplebees-date-night-pass-sold-out-minute-restaurant-food-meal-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDate%20Night%20Pass%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20sold%20out%20within%20minutes%2C%20a%20%240.50%20boneless%20wing%20promotion%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20the%20Dollarita.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeyton%20said%20it%20was%20important%20that%20Applebee's%20promotions%20were%20both%20profitable%20as%20a%20stand-alone%20and%20led%20to%20customers%20buying%20other%20things%20from%20its%20menu%2C%20too.%20He%20noted%20that%20Applebee's%20even%20makes%20a%20profit%20when%20it%20sells%20margaritas%20for%20%241%20under%20its%20Dollarita%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Applebee's%20trying%20to%20grab%20some%20cash-strapped%20fast-food%20customers%20by%20promoting%20value%20deals.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchain-restaurants-vs-fast-food-value-wars-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChili's%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20a%20%26quot%3B3%20For%20Me%26quot%3B%20combo%20that%20includes%20an%20appetizer%2C%20an%20entr%C3%A9e%20with%20a%20side%2C%20and%20a%20bottomless%20drink%20for%20%2410.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e703fac0-54d1-4b31-ac7b-46219fc79aaa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EApplebee's%20diners%20are%20cutting%20back%2C%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20casual%20dining%20chains%20have%20been%20raising%20their%20prices%2C%20too%2C%20because%20of%20wage%20and%20food%20inflation.%20At%20Dine%20Brands'%20restaurants%2C%20prices%20%26quot%3Bspiked%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20last%20roughly%20two%20years%2C%20rising%20by%20between%20about%205%25%20and%209%25%20on%20an%20annualized%20basis%2C%20Peyton%20said.%20Historically%2C%20its%20franchisees%20had%20put%20up%20prices%20by%20roughly%202%25%20to%203%25%20a%20year%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeyton%20warned%20that%20diners%20at%20Applebee's%20and%20sister%20company%20IHOP%20were%20switching%20to%20cheaper%20menu%20items%20and%20dining%20out%20less%20often.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20continue%20to%20see%20guests%20trade%20down%20from%20higher-priced%20items%20at%20both%20IHOP%20and%20Applebee's%2C%20another%20indicator%20that%20guests%20are%20managing%20their%20wallet%2C%26quot%3B%20Peyton%20told%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiners%20earning%20%2450%2C000%20and%20less%20were%20cutting%20back%20the%20most%20at%20both%20brands%2C%20Peyton%20said%2C%20