n%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JJP's%20chief%20media%20coordinator%2C%20Deepkamal%20Saharan%2C%20said%20members%20have%20to%20obey%20the%20party%20whip%20or%20get%20thrown%20out.%20%26quot%3BIn%20various%20constituencies%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20JJP%20MLAs%20working%20with%20BJP%20leaders.%20If%20they%20shift%20party%2C%20they%20also%20have%20to%20face%20infighting%20by%20the%20BJP's%20local%20cadre%20and%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20they%20would%20be%20accepted%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20pointing%20to%20an%20issue%20various%20leaders%20have%20faced%20after%20crossover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20Haryana%20was%20plunged%20into%20crisis%20earlier%20this%20week%20as%20MLAs%20Sombir%20Sangwan%20(representing%20Dadri)%2C%20Randhir%20Singh%20Gollen%20(from%20Pundri)%2C%20and%20Dharampal%20Gonder%20(of%20Nilokheri)%20stopped%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20press%20conference%20by%20Mr%20Chautala%20where%20he%2C%20accompanied%20by%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20declared%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20now%20a%20minority%20and%20he%20would%20provide%20outside%20support%20the%20Congress%20should%20they%20choose%20to%20form%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chautala%20chased%20it%20up%20with%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Governor%2C%20demanding%20a%20floor%20test%20in%20the%20assembly.%20But%20there%20he%20ran%20up%20against%20a%20technicality%20--%20only%20one%20no-confidence%20motion%20can%20be%20brought%20against%20the%20government%20in%20a%20single%20assembly%20session.%20The%20Congress%20had%20brought%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%20February%20and%20a%20floor%20test%20was%20held%20in%20March%2C%20during%20the%20budget%20session%20of%C2%A0%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20next%20assembly%20session%20will%20be%20the%20monsoon%20session%20in%20July%2C%20the%20Opposition's%20options%20are%20limited.%20The%20Governor%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20seek%20a%20special%20session%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20his%20call.%20INLD%20MLA%20Abhay%20Singh%20Chautala%20has%20also%20written%20to%20the%20Governor%2C%20saying%20if%20an%20assembly%20session%20cannot%20be%20called%2C%20President's%20Rule%20should%20immediately%20be%20imposed%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20assembly%20elections%20due%20later%20this%20year%20--%20the%20term%20of%20the%20assembly%20ends%20in%20November%20--%20toppling%20the%20Saini%20government%20could%20largely%20be%20an%20exercise%20in%20optics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Congress%20asked%20the%20Governor%20for%20an%20appointment%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20the%20party%20is%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20hurry%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BLess%20than%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20we%20won%20the%20trust%20vote.%20Now%2C%20when%20the%20session%20happens%2C%20we%20will%20talk.%20These%20people%20(the%20Congress)%20should%20focus%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saini%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715258280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F9sohp6l_dushyant-chautala_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-haryana-crisis-4-mlas-of-dushyant-chautala-meet-bjps-ml-khattar-5625319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dushyant%20Chautala%2C%20the%20friend-turned-foe%20of%20the%20BJP%20who%20is%20out%20to%20fell%20the%20government%2C%20should%20police%20his%20party%2C%20sources%20have%20indicated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-haryana-crisis-4-mlas-of-dushyant-chautala-meet-bjps-ml-khattar-5625319%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-haryana-crisis-4-mlas-of-dushyant-chautala-meet-bjps-ml-khattar-5625319%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news