al%20leader%20has%20ever%20been%20granted%20bail%20for%20campaigning%20and%20said%20that%20letting%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20out%20of%20jail%20to%20canvas%20for%20his%20party%20candidates%20would%20set%20a%20wrong%20precedent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20the%20petition%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20elected%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%20and%20is%20not%20a%20habitual%20offender.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20elections...%20these%20are%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20and%20he%20is%20not%20a%20habitual%20offender%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20affidavit%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20pointed%20out%20that%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%20bail%20plea%20of%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20-%20a%20co-accused%20in%20the%20case%20-%20the%20court%20had%20said%20that%20the%20laws%20apply%20equally%20to%20all%20citizens%20and%20institutions%2C%20including%20the%20State.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20sought%20interim%20bail%20primarily%20for%20campaigning%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20agency%20submitted%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20relevant%20to%20note%20that%20the%20right%20to%20campaign%20is%20neither%20a%20fundamental%20right%20nor%20a%20constitutional%20right%20and%20not%20even%20a%20legal%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20has%20argued%20that%20123%20elections%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%20and%20if%20interim%20bail%20is%20granted%20for%20campaigning%2C%20then%20no%20politician%20can%20be%20kept%20in%20judicial%20custody%20since%20polls%20take%20place%20around%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeating%20an%20argument%20it%20had%20made%20during%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20the%20ED%20said%20that%20campaigning%20is%20part%20of%20a%20politician's%20job%20and%2C%20following%20the%20rule%20of%20equality%2C%20small%20farmers%20or%20small%20traders%20can%20also%20seek%20interim%20bail%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20demands%20of%20their%20work.%C2%A0It%20also%20stressed%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20not%20even%20contesting%20the%20ongoing%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20petitioner%20(Arvind%20Kejriwal)%20is%20extended%20any%20interim%20relief%20on%20grounds%20of%20him%20being%20a%20politician%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20campaigning%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20for%20his%20party%2C%20there%20is%20no%20gain%20saying%20that%20all%20politicians%20incarcerated%20in%20one%20case%20or%20the%20other%20would%20not%20seek%20similar%20treatment%20that%20all%20politicians%20are%20a%20class%20of%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20states%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20granting%20bail%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20would%20set%20a%20precedent%20which%20would%20permit%20%26quot%3Ball%20unscrupulous%20politicians%26quot%3B%20to%20commit%20crimes%20and%20then%20evade%20investigation%20citing%20campaigning%20for%20one%20election%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExceptional%20Circumstance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20it%20could%20pass%20an%20order%20for%20interim%20bail%20and%20was%20not%20going%20by%20whether%20the%20petitioner%20is%20a%20politician%20or%20not.%20The%20focus%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20was%20on%20whether%20there%20was%20an%20exceptional%20circumstance%20which%20necessitated%20interim%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20asked%20the%20agency%20why%20it%20took%20them%20two%20years%20to%20act%20against%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20party.%20%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20is%20that%20it%20has%20taken%20two%20years%20for%20this.%20It%20is%20not%20good%20for%20any%20investigating%20agency%20to%20say%20that%20it%20takes%20two%20years%20to%20unearth...%20n