n-overseas-bank-clocks-q4-consolidated-pat-of-rs-810-42-cr-124050900810_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Belgium%20Teen%20Gang-Raped%20By%20Minors%2C%20Youngest%20Offender%20Is%20Aged%2011%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20disturbing%20case%20that%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20across%20Belgium%2C%20a%C2%A014-year-old%20girl%20was%C2%A0gang-raped%20by%20ten%20of%20her%20boyfriend's%20friends%20in%20a%20forest.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brusselstimes.com%2Fbelgium%2F1038198%2Fminors-suspected-of-gang-rape-of-14-year-old-girl-youngest-perpetrator-aged-11%5C%22%3EBrussels%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eall%20the%20ten%20accused%C2%A0are%20believed%20to%20be%20minors%2C%20aged%20between%2011%20and%2016.%C2%A0%20As%20per%20prosecutors%2C%20the%20girl%20was%20abused%20by%20ten%20minors%20on%20up%20to%20three%20occasions%20between%20April%202%20and%20April%206%20over%20the%20Easter%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20named%20for%20privacy%20reasons%2C%20was%20allegedly%20lured%20into%20a%20wooded%20area%20called%20Kabouterbos%20in%20Kortrijk%2C%20West%20Flanders%20(five%20miles%20from%20the%20French%20border)%2C%20by%20her%20teenage%20boyfriend%20over%20the%20Easter%20school%20break.%20She%20was%C2%A0abused%20by%20several%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20with%20some%20sources%20stating%20she%20was%20kept%20there%20for%20two%20days.%20The%20group%20also%20filmed%20the%20attack%20on%20their%20smartphones%20and%20posted%20clips%20to%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20took%20turns%20abusing%20the%20victim%2C%20and%20all%20participated%20'to%20a%20greater%20or%20lesser%20extent%2C'%20Belgian%20outlet%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nieuwsblad.be%2Fcnt%2Fdmf20240508_96180261%5C%22%3ENieuwsblad%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20in%20its%20report.%C2%A0%C2%A0None%20of%20the%20group%20urged%20their%20friends%20to%20stop%20the%20abuse%2C%20sources