%2C%20Suma%20and%20Rohit%20invested%20Rs%204.2%20lakh%20in%20installing%20the%20RWH%20setup%2C%20which%20required%20digging%2C%20masonry%2C%20waterproofing%20of%20the%20tank%2C%20and%20plumbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20never%20a%20time%20when%20I%20doubted%20investing%20Rs%204.5%20lakh%20in%20RWH.%20We%20tried%20our%20best%20to%20build%20a%20sustainable%20house%20without%20any%20explicit%20expectation%20of%20return%20on%20investment%20to%20the%20extent%20we%20could%20afford%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suma%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlongside%20this%2C%20we%20also%20invested%20in%20solar%20panels%20and%20compressed%20mud%20blocks%20for%20the%20entire%20house%20that%20offer%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20adopting%20slightly%20sustainable%20choices.%20We%20also%20prefer%20using%20buckets%20over%20showers%20for%20bathing.%20We%20also%20have%20aerators%20for%20most%20of%20the%20faucets%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-5-1715150918.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rohit%20and%20Suma%20harvest%20rainwater%20for%20non-potable%20purposes%20like%20cleaning%2C%20bathing%2C%20and%20gardening%20needs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-5-1715150918.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-5-1715150918-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-5-1715150918-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-5-1715150918-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-wa