ment%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsikandar-fans-call-salman-khan-rashmika-mandannas-jodi-blockbuster%2Farticleshow%2F109980809.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Eurovision%20contestant%20Eden%20Golan%20booed%20during%20rehearsal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715251750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fa1e1%2Flive%2F6bfd5b60-0de6-11ef-bee9-6125e244a4cd.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcjewg9enx27o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eden%20Golan%20was%20performing%20her%20song%20Hurricane%20at%20a%20dress%20rehearsal%20when%20she%20was%20booed%20by%20the%20crowd.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3138%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcjewg9enx27o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcjewg9enx27o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcjewg9enx27o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindu%20Population%20Fell%207.8%25%20Between%201950-2015%2C%20Muslims%20Up%2043.15%25%3A%20PM's%20Panel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20of%20the%20Hindu%20population%20decreased%20by%207.82%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015%20in%20India%2C%20while%20that%20of%20Muslims%20increased%20by%2043.15%20per%20cent%2C%20suggesting%20that%20there%20is%20a%20conducive%20environment%20in%20the%20country%20to%20foster%20diversity%2C%20said%20a%20recent%20working%20paper%20by%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20titled%20'Share%20of%20Religious%20Minorities%3A%20A%20Cross-Country%20Analysis%20(1950-2015)'%20further%20said%20the%20share%20of%20Jains%20in%20the%20population%20of%20India%20decreased%20from%200.45%20per%20cent%20in%201950%20to%200.36%20per%20cent%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20Hindu%20population%20decreased%20by%207.82%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015%20(from%2084.68%20per%20cent%20to%2078.06%20per%20cent).%20The%20share%20of%20Muslim%20population%20in%201950%20was%209.84%20per%20cent%20and%20increased%20to%2014.09%20per%20cent%20in%202015%20--%20a%2043.15%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20their%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20paper%20prepared%20by%20a%20team%20led%20by%20Shamika%20Ravi%2C%20member%2C%20EAC-PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20paper%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Christian%20population%20rose%20from%202.24%20per%20cent%20to%202.36%20per%20cent%20--%20an%20increase%20of%205.38%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20share%20of%20Sikh%20population%20increased%20from%201.24%20per%20cent%20in%201950%20to%201.85%20per%20cent%20in%202015%20-%20a%206.58%20per%20cent%20rise%20in%20their%20share%2C%20the%20share%20of%20the%20Parsi%20population%20in%20India%20witnessed%20a%20stark%2085%20per%20cent%20decline%2C%20reducing%20from%200.03%20per%20cent%20share%20in%201950%20to%200.004%20per%20cent%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20indicates%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20a%20conducive%20environment%20to%20foster%20diversity%20in%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20paper%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20promote%20better%20life%20outcomes%20for%20the%20disadvantaged%20sections%20of%20society%20without%20providing%20a%20nurturing%20environment%20and%20societal%20support%20through%20a%20bottom-up%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20noted%20that%20a%20decrease%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20population%20and%20a%20consequent%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20minorities%20suggests%20that%20the%20net%20result%20of%20all%20policy%20actions%2C%20political%20decisions%20and%20societal%20processes%20is%20to%20provide%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20increasing%20diversity%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20global%20trends%20of%20declining%20majority%2C%20India%20too%20has%20witnessed%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20by%207.82%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20particularly%20remarkable%20given%20the%20wider%20context%20within%20the%20South%20Asian%20neighborhood%20where%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20has%20increased%20and%20minority%20populations%20have%20shrunk%20alarmingly%20across%20countries%20like%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20said%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%2C%20therefore%2C%20minority%20populations%20from%20across%20the%20neighborhood%20come%20to%20India%20during%20times%20of%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20pointed%20out%20that%20all%20the%20Muslim%20majority%20countries%20witnessed%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20except%20Maldives%2C%20where%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20group%20(Shafi'i%20Sunnis)%20declined%20by%201.47%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bangladesh%2C%20there%20was%20an%2018%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20group%20which%20is%20the%20largest%20such%20increase%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%20Pakistan%20witnessed%20an%20increase%20of%203.75%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20(Hanafi%20Muslim)%20and%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20total%20Muslim%20population%20despite%20the%20creation%20of%20Bangladesh%20in%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20among%20non-Muslim%20majority%20countries%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20India%20and%20Nepal%20saw%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20noted%20that%20the%20year%201950%20is%20important%20as%20a%20baseline%20year%20for%20two%20major%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20around%20the%20time%20that%20the%20international%20human%20rights%20framework%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20newly%20created%20United%20Nations%20began%20to%20take%20shape%20with%20minority%20rights%20and%20state%20responsibility%20for%20protection%20of%20minorities%20being%20mainstreamed%20in%20international%20law%2C%20the%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20is%20a%20detailed%20cross-country%20descriptive%20analysis%20of%20the%20status%20of%20minorities%20around%20the%20world%20measured%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20changing%20share%20in%20a%20country's%20population%20over%2065%20years%20between%201950%20and%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20167%20countries%20analysed%2C%20the%20average%20value%20for%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20in%20the%20baseline%20year%20of%201950%20is%2075%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20the%20mean%20of%20the%20distribution%20capturing%20the%20change%20in%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20between%201950%20and%202015%20is%2021.9.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715251740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fjrmv5a_population-generic-india-ians_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-population-fell-7-8-between-1950-2015-muslims-up-43-15-centres-report-5624094%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hindu%20population%20fell%20by%207.82%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015%20in%20India%2C%20while%20that%20of%20Muslims%20increased%20by%2043.15%20per%20cent%2C%20suggesting%20that%20there%20is%20a%20conducive%20environment%20in%20the%20country%20to%20foster%20diversity%2C%20said%20a%20recent%20working%20paper%20by%20the%20Centre.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-population-fell-7-8-between-1950-2015-muslims-up-43-15-centres-report-5624094%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-population-fell-7-8-between-1950-2015-muslims-up-43-15-centres-report-5624094%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-population-fell-7-8-between-1950-2015-muslims-up-43-15-centres-report-5624094%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Controversy%20After%20Video%20Seems%20To%20Show%20BJP%20Leader's%20Minor%20Son%20Casting%20Vote%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EControversy%20has%20erupted%20after%20a%20video%20emerged%20online%20today%20showing%20a%20minor%20boy%20seeming%20to%20cast%20a%20vote%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Berasia%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Bhopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20boy%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Vinay%20Mehar%2C%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20panchayat%20leader%2C%20and%20he%20accompanied%20his%20father%20-%20who%20seemed%20to%20take%20the%20video%20-%20into%20the%20polling%20booth%20during%20voting%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20cast%20the%20vote%2C%20on%20his%20father's%20behalf%2C%20on%20the%20EVM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2014-second%20video%20-%20reportedly%20shared%20on%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20Facebook%20page%20-%20was%20flagged%20by%20the%20media%20advisor%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath.%20The%20video%20shows%20the%20boy%20and%20the%20father%20in%20the%20booth%20and%20pressing%20a%20button%20on%20the%20EVM%20linked%20to%20the%20lotus%2C%20or%20the%20BJP's%20symbol.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20camera%20then%20pans%20to%20show%20the%20vote%20being%20registered%20by%20the%20VVPAT%2C%20or%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20machine%2C%20after%20which%20Mr%20Mehar%20is%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BOk.%20That%20is%20enough%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20have%20asked%20about%20how%20a)%20a%20mobile%20phone%20was%20allowed%20into%20the%20polling%20booth%2C%20and%20b)%20how%20the%20child%20was%20permitted%20to%20accompany%20his%20father%20into%20the%20booth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20has%20turned%20the%20Election%20Commission%20into%20a%20child's%20plaything.%20In%20Bhopal%2C%20the%20BJP's%20district%20panchayat%20member%20Vinay%20Mehar%20got%20his%20minor%20son%20to%20cast%20his%20vote.%20Vinay%20Mehar%20also%20made%20a%20video%20of%20the%20time%20when%20he%20cast%20his%20vote.%20Vinay%20Mehar%20posted%20the%20video%20on%20Facebook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20there%20be%20any%20action%3F%26quot%3B%20Piyush%20Babele%2C%20whose%20X%20handle%20describes%20him%20as%20a%20media%20advisor%20in%20the%20office%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20said%20as%20he%20shared%20the%20video%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20been%20acknowledged%20by%20district%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Collector%20Kaushalendra%20Vikram%20Singh%20has%20ordered%20an%20investigation.%20Presiding%20Officer%20Sandeep%20Saini%20has%20been%20suspended%20and%20a%20FIR%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Berasia%20Assembly%20segment%2C%20where%20the%20incident%20took%20place%2C%20is%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Caste%20candidates%2C%20and%20is%20one%20of%20eight%20that%20makes%20up%20the%20Bhopal%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Berasia%20segment%20is%20held%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Vishnu%20Khatre%2C%20while%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20held%20by%20the%20party's%20Pragya%20Thakur%2C%20who%20thumped%20the%20Congress'%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20in%20the%20last%20election.%20She%20will%20not%2C%20though%2C%20defend%20her%20seat%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20Alok%20Sharma%20against%20the%20Congress'%20Arun%20Shrivastava.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715251680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbm3edjvg_minor-voting-_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontroversy-after-video-seems-to-show-bjp-leaders-minor-son-casting-vote-5624579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Controversy%20has%20erupted%20after%20a%20video%20surfaced%20online%20today%20showing%20a%20minor%20boy%20seeming%20to%20cast%20a%20vote%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Berasia%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Bhopal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontroversy-after-video-seems-to-show-bjp-leaders-minor-son-casting-vote-5624579%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontroversy-after-video-seems-to-show-bjp-leaders-minor-son-casting-vote-5624579%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontroversy-after-video-seems-to-show-bjp-leaders-minor-son-casting-vote-5624579%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TCS%20CEO%20K%20Krithivasan%20got%20Rs%2025.2%20crore%20remuneration%20in%20FY24%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715251653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109980635%2Cimgsize-1480567.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Ftcs-ceo-k-krithivasan-got-rs-25-2-crore-remuneration-in-fy24%2Farticleshow%2F109980715.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TCS%20CEO%20K%20Krithivasan%20earned%20Rs%2025.2%20crore%20in%202024%2C%20lower%20than%20ex-CEO%20Rajesh%20Gopinathan.%20N%20G%20Subramaniam%2C%20COO%2C%20earned%20Rs%2026.1%20crore.%20TCS's%20revenue%20reached%20Rs%20240%2C893%20crore%20with%20an%20operating%20margin%20of%2024.6%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Ftcs-ceo-k-krithivasan-got-rs-25-2-crore-remuneration-in-fy24%2Farticleshow%2F109980715.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TCS%20CEO%20Takes%20Home%20Rs%2025.36%20Crore%2C%20COO%20Got%20Rs%2026.18%20Crore%20In%202023-24%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EK%20Krithivasan%2C%20the%20newly%20appointed%20chief%20executive%20officer%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20TCS%2C%20took%20home%20a%20pay%20of%20over%20Rs%2025%20crore%20in%20FY24%2C%20the%20company%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Krithivasan%20took%20charge%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20IT%20services%20exporter%20in%20June%202023%2C%20after%20the%20surprising%20exit%20of%20Rajesh%20Gopinathan.%20His%20appointment%20is%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20company's%20annual%20report%2C%20Mr%20Krithivasan%20earned%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201.27%20crore%2C%20with%20benefits%2C%20perquisites%20and%20allowances%20of%20Rs%203.08%20crore%20and%20bagged%20a%20commission%20of%20Rs%2021%20crore%20during%20the%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earnings%20include%20his%20compensation%20as%20the%20global%20head%20of%20the%20largest%20vertical%20of%20banking%2C%20financial%20services%20and%20insurance%20at%20TCS%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20company%2C%20NG%20Subramaniam%20earned%20Rs%2026.18%20crore%20during%20the%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Subramaniam%2C%20who%20is%20due%20to%20retire%20from%20the%20company%20soon%2C%20was%20in%20the%20role%20for%20the%20entire%20year%20and%20his%20emoluments%20included%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201.72%20crore%3B%20Rs%203.45%20crore%20in%20benefits%2C%20perquisites%20and%20allowances%2C%20and%20Rs%2021%20crore%20in%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20COO's%20remuneration%20increased%20by%208.2%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20company%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20Mr%20Krithivasan's%20earnings%20cannot%20be%20compared%20because%20of%20the%20change%20in%20the%20designation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20two%20months%20of%20service%20as%20CEO%20Gopinathan%20earned%20Rs%2033.6%20lakh%20in%20salary%20and%20Rs%2076.8%20lakh%20in%20benefits%2C%20perquisites%20and%20allowances%2C%20the%20annual%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20COO's%20remuneration%20is%20346.2%20times%20the%20median%20remuneration%20of%20its%20employees%2C%20which%20stood%20at%20Rs%206%2C01%2C546%20as%20of%20March%2031%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20annual%20increase%20was%20in%20the%20range%20of%205.5-8%20per%20cent%2C%20with%20top%20performers%20receiving%20double-digit%20increments%20in%20India%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20constituted%2035.6%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20workforce%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20fiscal%2C%20the%20company%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20which%20was%20among%20the%20first%20ones%20in%20the%20sector%20to%20nudge%20employees%20to%20shift%20back%20to%20working%20from%20offices%2C%20has%20approximately%2055%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20employees%20working%20from%20the%20office%20on%20all%20working%20days%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20report%20said%20there%20is%20near-term%20uncertainty%20for%20the%20business%20because%20of%20a%20slew%20of%20global%20headwinds%2C%20but%20stressed%20that%20there%20is%20growth%20visibility%20over%20the%20medium%20to%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20report%20said%20the%20overall%20revenue%20growth%20slowed%20down%20to%206.8%20per%20cent%20in%20FY24%20from%2017.6%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20delayed%20decision-making%20and%20cash%20conservation%20seen%20in%20some%20segments%20through%20FY%202024%20continues%20into%20the%20next%20fiscal%20year%2C%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20moderation%20in%20growth%20in%20FY%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20annual%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20chairman%20N%20Chandrasekaran%20said%20GenAI%20technologies%20will%20impact%20almost%20every%20sector%20and%20the%20country%20going%20forward%20and%20enterprises%20have%20already%20invested%20in%20cloud%2C%20data%20infrastructure%20and%20large%20processing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenAI%20will%20not%20only%20improve%20productivity%20but%20also%20create%20an%20impact%20we%20hitherto%20have%20not%20seen%20or%20imagined%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Krithivasan%20said%20the%20all-time%20high%20order%20book%2C%20continued%20deal%20flow%20and%20pipeline%20velocity%20give%20it%20confidence%20in%20business%20momentum%2C%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20greater%20opportunities%20ahead%2C%20as%20businesses%20become%20more%20technology-intensive%20and%20depend%20on%20technology%20to%20drive%20competitive%20differentiation%20and%20transform%20their%20industries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20TCS%20were%20trading%200.45%20per%20cent%20lower%20at%20Rs%203%2C954.80%20apiece%20on%20the%20BSE%2C%20as%20against%201.23%20per%20cent%20correction%20on%20the%20benchmark%20at%201443%20hrs.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715251440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-08%2Ftcs-650-400_650x400_71470764051.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftcs-ceo-k-krithivasan-takes-home-rs-25-36-crore-coo-ng-subramaniam-got-rs-26-18-crore-in-2023-24-5624308%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22K%20Krithivasan%2C%20the%20newly%20appointed%20chief%20executive%20officer%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20TCS%2C%20took%20home%20a%20pay%20of%20over%20Rs%2025%20crore%20in%20FY24%2C%20the%20company%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftcs-ceo-k-krithivasan-takes-home-rs-25-36-crore-coo-ng-subramaniam-got-rs-26-18-crore-in-2023-24-5624308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftcs-ceo-k-krithivasan-takes-home-rs-25-36-crore-coo-ng-subramaniam-got-rs-26-18-crore-in-2023-24-5624308%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftcs-ceo-k-krithivasan-takes-home-rs-25-36-crore-coo-ng-subramaniam-got-rs-26-18-crore-in-2023-24-5624308%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Endangered%20Whale%20Dead%20After%20Collision%20With%20Cruise%20Ship%20Off%20New%20York%20Port%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20rare%20and%20endangered%20whale%20died%20likely%20due%20to%20a%20collision%20with%20a%20cruise%20ship%20as%20it%20approached%C2%A0New%20York%20City's%20Port%20of%20Brooklyn%20over%20the%20weekend.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F05%2F08%2Fus-news%2Fendangered-whale-likely-killed-by-massive-msc-meraviglia-cruise-ship-en-route-to-nyc%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%2044-foot%20whale%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20cruise%20ship%20MSC%20Meraviglia%20in%20the%20Port%20of%20Brooklyn%20on%20May%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20necropsy%2C%20the%20animal%20equivalent%20of%20an%20autopsy%2C%20identified%20the%20marine%20mammal%20as%20a%20mature%20female%20sei%20whale%2C%20an%20endangered%20species%20typically%20found%20in%20deep%20waters%20far%20from%20land%2C%20the%20Atlantic%20Marine%20Conservation%20Society%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20revealed%20evidence%20of%20tissue%20trauma%20along%20the%20whale's%20right%20shoulder%20blade%20region%20and%20a%20right%20flipper%20fracture.%20The%20creature's%20gastrointestinal%20tract%20was%20also%20full%20of%20food.%20Most%20of%20the%20whale's%20organs%20were%20sampled%2C%20along%20with%20tissue%20and%20bone%2C%20for%20toxicology%20and%20pathology%20analysis%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMSC%20Cruises%2C%20the%20company%20that%20owns%20the%20ship%2C%C2%A0confirmed%20the%20whale%20was%20found%20on%20the%20bow%20of%20its%20ship%20as%20it%20approached%20the%20Port%20of%20New%20York%2C%20and%20said%20the%20company%20notified%20authorities%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20loss%20of%20any%20marine%20life.%20We%20have%20comprehensive%20measures%20in%20place%20to%20help%20avoid%20collisions%2C%20such%20as%20training%20all%20our%20deck%20officers%20with%20the%20Ocean%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Conservation%20Association%20(ORCA)%20and%20we%20follow%20regulations%20designed%20to%20protect%20whales%20and%20other%20marine%20life.%20This%20includes%20altering%20itineraries%20in%20certain%20regions%20to%20avoid%20whales%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20evaluate%20and%20update%20our%20procedures%20with%20our%20partners%20and%20the%20authorities%2C%20''%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERob%20DiGiovanni%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20chief%20scientist%20of%20the%20Atlantic%20Marine%20Conservation%20Society%2C%20told%20The%20Post%20it%20was%20more%20than%20likely%20that%20the%20''interaction%20with%20the%20vessel%20contributed%20to%20her%20death.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fisheries.noaa.gov%2Fspecies%2Fsei-whale%5C%22%3ENational%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Sei%20whales%20can%20grow%20to%20be%20up%20to%2060%20feet%20long%20and%20have%20a%20lifespan%20of%2050%20to%2070%20years.%20They%20are%20known%20as%20exceptionally%20fast%20swimmers%2C%20capable%20of%20reaching%20speeds%20of%20more%20than%2034%20miles%20per%20hour%20(55kph).%C2%A0They%20dwell%20mostly%20in%20subtropical%2C%20temperate%20and%20subpolar%20seas%20around%20the%20world%2C%20primarily%20the%20Atlantic%2C%20Indian%20and%20Pacific%20oceans.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThese%20whales%20used%20to%20be%20abundant%20in%20the%20US%20and%20around%20the%20world%2C%20but%20up%20to%20300%2C000%20of%20them%20were%20killed%20by%20commercial%20whalers%20in%20the%2019th%20and%2020th%20centuries%2C%20according%20to%20NOAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715251080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fv0r1qlu8_sei-whale_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fendangered-whale-dead-after-collision-with-cruise-ship-off-new-york-port-report-5624861%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20necropsy%2C%20the%20animal%20equivalent%20of%20an%20autopsy%2C%20identified%20the%20deceased%20marine%20mammal%20as%20a%20mature%20female%20sei%20whale%2C%20an%20endangered%20species%20typically%20found%20in%20deep%20waters%20far%20from%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fendangered-whale-dead-after-collision-with-cruise-ship-off-new-york-port-report-5624861%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fendangered-whale-dead-after-collision-with-cruise-ship-off-new-york-port-report-5624861%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fendangered-whale-dead-after-collision-with-cruise-ship-off-new-york-port-report-5624861%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20Just%20Rs%202000%2C%20Sponsor%20An%20Entire%20Year%20of%20Education%20for%20Kids%20of%20Migrant%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPausing%20her%20lengthy%20evening%20routine%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20Ishita%20swiftly%20heads%20to%20her%20favourite%20spot%3A%20Juin%20Madam%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20where%20she%20eagerly%20joins%20me%20on%20a%20video%20call.%20Despite%20the%20crackling%20sound%20of%20a%20poor%20network%2C%20her%20enthusiasm%20shines%20through%20as%20she%20exclaims%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20truly%20a%20blessing%20to%20be%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshita%20is%20a%20student%20enrolled%20at%20Pathshala%2C%20a%20foundation%20led%20by%20Juin%20Datta%20in%20Vadodara.%20This%20organisation%20is%20committed%20to%20offering%20free%20education%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282848%2Fretired-teacher-gives-free-education-to-children-in-jammu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20those%20from%20migrant%20workers%E2%80%99%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20a%20comprehensive%20range%20of%20essentials%20to%20our%20students%20here%20%E2%80%94%20from%20quality%20education%2C%20shelter%2C%20food%2C%20and%20clothing%20to%20promising%20opportunities%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20stigma%20attached%20to%20joining%20school%20late%20because%20we%20operate%20differently%20from%20conventional%20schools.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20project-based%20learning%2C%20the%20school%20eschews%20traditional%20grading%20systems%20in%20favour%20of%20levels.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20I%20might%20be%20at%20Level%204%20for%20Gujarati%20but%20Level%208%20for%20math.%20Age%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a