E2%80%98working%20water%E2%80%99.%20Interestingly%2C%20while%20hydroponics%20has%20gained%20popularity%20today%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20around%20since%20time%20immemorial%3B%20seen%20even%20in%20the%20Hanging%20Gardens%20of%20Babylon%20and%20the%20floating%20gardens%20of%20the%20Aztecs%20in%20Mexico%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20technology%2C%20greenhouses%2C%20scientists%20have%20developed%20some%20tools%20and%20systems%20to%20make%20it%20effective%20and%20efficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERasik%20uses%20the%20method%20of%20vertical%20farming%20by%20employing%20the%20Nutrient%20Film%20Technique%20(NFT).%20This%20technique%20uses%20pumps%20to%20circulate%20a%20thin%20film%20of%20nutrient%20solution%20through%20shallow%20channels%2C%20where%20plant%20roots%20can%20dip%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327451%2Fdr-vp-sethi-punjab-agri-university-hybrid-hydroponics-helps-reduce-water-wastage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceive%20nutrients%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Pure%20Greens%20container%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advantage%20of%20this%20technique%2C%20he%20states%2C%20is%20the%20usage%20of%20less%20water%20and%20space%20to%20enhance%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESave%20water%2C%20no%20soil%20to%20get%20maximum%20yield%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Rasik%20mastered%20the%20art%20of%20hydroponics%2C%20his%20terrace%20drew%20hundreds%20of%20visitors%20in%20Rajkot%2C%20including%20scientists.%20The%20increased%20interest%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20awareness%20programs%20and%20his%20training%20centre%2C%20One%20Farm%20Hydroponics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fras