en%20grows%20more%20than%20250%20varieties%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPrescription%20for%20a%20long%20healthy%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20childhood%2C%20Naveen%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20vegetables%20and%20fruit%20trees%20that%20were%20nurtured%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346317%2Fassam-organic-farmer-neelam-dutta-conserves-climate-resilient-heirloom-seeds-pabhoi-greens-northeast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enative%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20growing%20up%20he%20understood%20that%20these%20seeds%20were%20fast%20disappearing%20due%20to%20modernisation%20and%20hunger%20for%20harvesting%20more%20produce%20in%20less%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20see%20only%20green-coloured%20ladyfingers%20in%20the%20market%20when%20there%20are%20several%20native%20variants%20including%20the%20red-coloured%20torpedo%20shaped%20variety%20and%20light%20green-coloured%20long%20elephant%20tusk%20variety%20that%20has%20more%20amount%20of%20amino%20acids%20and%20iron%20content.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20get%20only%20hybrid%20tomatoes%20even%20though%20we%20have%20more%20than%20200%20native%20tomato%20varieties%20with%20distinct%20tastes%20and%20nutritional%20content.%20Irrespective%20of%20their%20benefits%2C%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20those%20vegetables%20in%20markets%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20where%20have%20these%20vegetables%20disappeared%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20eat%20only%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20varieties.%20Genetically%20modified%20seeds%20only%20respond%20to%20chemical%20insecticides%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naveen%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20can%20reduce%20this%20dependency%20by%20growing%20our%20own%20vegetables.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3