rrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Finnovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20impact%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20are%20having%20on%20someone%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20livelihood%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20believed%20something%20%E2%80%9Cmagical%E2%80%9D%20would%20come%20out%20of%20such%20an%20initiative%3B%20something%20that%20surpassed%20money.%20As%20they%20look%20back%20on%20the%20journey%20of%20disbursing%20over%20Rs%20154%2C22%2C50%2C680%20in%20the%2016%20years%20that%20they%20have%20been%20active%2C%20they%20say%20it%20has%20exceeded%20their%20expectations%20of%20the%20power%20of%20a%20project%20of%20this%20scope.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20of%20their%20most%20recent%20projects%20is%20empowering%20the%20rickshaw%20community%20in%20Matheran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENot%20a%20crowdfunding%20campaign%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Matheran%20e-Auto%20Rickshaw%20Fund%E2%80%99%20lets%20you%20invest%20in%20hand-rickshaw-pullers%20in%20Matheran%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20upgrade%20to%20e-rickshaws%20and%20earn%20higher%20incomes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20credit%20will%20ensure%20them%20a%20life%20away%20from%20the%20drudgery%20and%20hard%20work%20of%20pulling%20rickshaws%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20on%20the%20mud%20roads%20of%20Matheran.%20The%20money%20will%20be%20channelled%20towards%20them%20buying%20e-rickshaws%20and%20your%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336102%2Fpimpri-chinchwad-maharashtra-wins-medal-for-urban-innovation-by-ias-shekhar-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ram%20says%2C%20can%20enable%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20per%20month%20for%20these%20hand-rickshaw-pullers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5